This review highlights the key takeaways and ideas from some of the experts.

Andre Antoine is a driven, loyal and dedicated individual.
While Andre belongs to many entrepreneurial organizations, his primary role at Wealth Canada involves coaching and supporting a team of over 60 investment advisors across the country.
Andre is primarily focused on relationships. Whether they be within his “crew”, his personal family or his entire extended network, Andre believes in building strong, lasting relationships that can positively impact everyone he meets. One of the core tenets of a successful business is networking and this is a focus from day one, whether it be professionals such as lawyers, accountants and other referral partners or clients.
